Step 7 — IAM Role Assignment

Gave Databricks access to BOTH storage accounts
Role: Storage Blob Data Contributor

Can read ✅ write ✅ delete ✅
Cannot manage storage settings ❌ (Principle of Least Privilege)


Done via: Storage Account → Access Control (IAM) → Add Role Assignment

